title: Gregory Forsberg
text: Hello, my name is Gregory Forsberg from Saint Paul, Minnesota. I’m currently a junior at Macalester College, majoring in Data Science. My interest lies at the intersection of data science and healthcare, where I explore how data-driven insights can transform and improve patient care and medical research.

title: Statistical analysis of PRRT treatment for Nen’s tumors
text:
An R/Shiny app that visualizes survival rates based on PRRT treatment for Neuroendocrine Tumors.
This app was created by my research group at University of Iowas Summer Institue of Biostatistics with the help of Dr.Patrick Breheny
Check out the app here.
